{"tid":2508230,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國遊戲商Nexon擲「1 億美元買BTC」！跑跑卡丁車、CSO母公司，買進 1,717 枚比特幣","createTime":"2021-04-28T14:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T17:21:57.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b6449d3ab5f5ceded755edb5d89a4b44f78ee06b","tid":2508230,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/image.blocktempo.com/2021/04/nexon-2-750x375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fimage.blocktempo.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fnexon-2-750x375.jpg&h=623aa588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上市公司買幣似乎已成為一股不可擋的潮流，繼特斯拉、美圖、MicroStrategy 等公司進場後，最新參戰的是韓國的遊戲公司 Nexon，也就是爆爆王、跑跑卡丁車以及 CSO 絕對武力的推出公司。<br />\n（前情提要：特斯拉脫手10%BTC！Q1比特幣出售「獲利超1億鎂」，馬斯克 : 為證明流動性，但我個人沒賣）<br />\n（事件背景：解讀｜除了美圖秀秀，為何上市公司狂買BTC不愛以太坊？機構會是ETH新支柱嗎？）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n韓國遊戲巨擘 Nexon 今（28）日宣布，買進 1,717 枚比特幣（截稿前價格 54,834 計算，約值 9,415 萬美元），扣除各種費用和支出成本後，比特幣買入成本平均約為每枚 58,226 美元，相當於 Nexon 手頭現金和現金價物總資產的 2%。成為繼特斯拉、美圖後最新一位買進比特幣的上市公司。<br />\n<br />\nNexon 的 CEO 歐文（Owen Mahoney）在聲明中表示，Nexon 購買比特幣，是為了保護股東資產價值和提升現金購買力。經過嚴格考量後，該公司認為在當今的經濟環境下，比特幣提供長期的穩定性和流動性，是最佳的選擇。<br />\n<br />\nNexon 成立於 1995 年，是韓國的老牌遊戲大廠，旗下作品包括爆爆王、CSO 絕對武力、跑跑卡丁車、新楓之谷以及艾爾之光等知名大作，個個都是 2000 年前後的年輕人幾乎必定玩過的遊戲；目前 Nexon 擁有超過 50 種線上遊戲，平台橫跨 PC 、智慧型手機，可在 190 多個國家／地區使用。<br />\n<br />\n2011 年時 Nexon 在日本上市，是當年度該股市最大的上市融資案，市值緊追在遊戲界龍頭任天堂（Nintendo）、暴雪（Blizzard）以及 EA（Electronic Arts）之後。<br />\n<br />\n上市公司紛紛進場買幣<br />\nNexon 並不是首家進場買幣的上市公司，同樣在列的還有電動車大廠特斯拉、圖片及影音應用程式開發商美圖、美國商業軟體公司 MicroStrategy、 支付巨擘 Square 等等。<br />\n<br />\n香港上市公司美圖在首次買幣時，就表達看好加密貨幣的升值空間，以作為分散現金風險的配置。特斯拉執行長也在今年買進 15 億美元比特幣後不久公開直言：「當法定貨幣的利率為負值的時候，只有傻瓜才不會往別處看。」<br />\n<br />\n全球最大主動管理型 ETF 的方舟投資管理公司（ARK Invest）分析師塔莎・基尼（Tasha Keeney）2 月 9 日接受《CNBC》專訪時便預測道，未來將會有更多企業加入買幣行列，將比特幣作為公司的儲備金使用。"},{"pid":"c6a63f6d13e9102edec286865cee5eaa55985524","tid":2508230,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"96628d91890e1bb7c2c2bc7c8805a12e3985dbc1","tid":2508230,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"crypto is scam <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1296fbd5b3a239a32de2e283d23468feceeb8f","tid":2508230,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"蘋果入場未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fb5568762230684deeb93f14b24a13561dbbb7","tid":2508230,"uid":385411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"買bitcoin賺嘅錢可能仲多啲整啲game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455e7a9952c437ec87506f4cf04cf277d94dd0d2","tid":2508230,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"Scam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e447edbcaf538954299bdde26df2d7d6e1ad2c0a","tid":2508230,"uid":286928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"自己出隻幣搞遊戲道具NFT唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c58f0fa69916b58b1f4743c93f36aba13a75e27","tid":2508230,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"原來間野咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bce1ef687b218a2ddf08c7ffdaec8c981ad604","tid":2508230,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"講nexon 都唔提瑪奇 哭能左"},{"pid":"2eba1684c788a7dcb77edeb8c496c1465b094221","tid":2508230,"uid":109098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到tesla執錢咁執<br />\n大家都想玩"}]}